Men's Health UK - August 2013 (pdf)

Mens Health is the UKs best-selling quality mens magazine packed with expert tips and advice on everything todays man needs to feel fitter, healthier, and happier. Every month Mens Health delivers the inside track on the subjects that matter most to men. Naturally theres fitness, weight loss and general health plus the best advice on food, nutrition and meal plans
